me experience the strength of multiple voices, races, cultures, beliefs, identities, orientations and points of view.    Life on campus  Experience Chicago              Illinois' Best Value  Our work continues  Watch here   We are  University of Illinois at Chicago           Luke Yaklich named UIC men’s basketball head coach                               UIC-Shakespeare Theater partnership supplies 5,000 masks to UI Health, leads to work for many                           Physics and mathematics student named Goldwater Scholar                  $8M to UIC to lead DOE materials research center                  We Are Accepting Undergraduate Applications      Visit Us Virtually      Request info      Apply now      Contact us          Campus Reminders    Returning library materials  Latest instructions for patrons on returns, settling accounts    Library Assistance and Resources  Library faculty and staff are available to help with learning, teaching and research          News     UIC College of Nursing, donors team up to celebrate UI Health nurses for National Nurses Week      UIC to hold virtual graduation celebration      South Shore clinic expands COVID-19 testing      $8M to UIC to lead DOE materials research center     More news    Events     May 4  Virtual Grad Fest  Interactive experience exclusively for the Class of 2020      May 12  Student Employment x UIC Life IG Takeover!  Student Employment shares tips on how to find jobs on-campus, who's currently hiring, and more      May 15  Calling for a Feminist Foreign Policy to Confront the Pandemic  Virtual event sponsored by the Women's Leadership and Resource Center     More events    Academic Dates    May 16  Spring commencement ceremonies by disciplinary college    May 18  Summer Session 1 (4-Week Session) Begins    May 20  Last day to complete late registration or add/drop courses for Summer Session 1    May 25  Memorial Day holiday, no classes    Academic calendar               1200 West Harrison St.  Chicag